<p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">神舟家族成功接力！</span></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">经管学子点赞神舟十八号载人航天飞船</span></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">20点59分搭载神舟十八号载人飞船的长征二号F遥十八运载火箭在酒泉卫星发射中心点火发射</span></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">约10分钟后</span></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">神舟十八号载人飞船与火箭成功分离</span></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">进入预定轨道</span></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240430/1714454279647064553.png" title="1714454279647064553.png" alt="微信截图_20240430130946.png" width="610" height="372" style="max-width: 100%; height: 372px; width: 610px;"/></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">震撼原声激动人心的一幕</span></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">此次任务是我国载人航天工程进入空间站应用与发展阶段的第3次载人飞行任务，是工程立项实施以来的第32次发射任务，也是长征系列运载火箭的第518次飞行。</span></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">在轨驻留期间，神十八乘组将迎来天舟八号货运飞船和神舟十九号载人飞船的来访，计划于今年10月下旬返回东风着陆场。</span></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">点赞中国航天！</span></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">中国航天事业再次迎来历史性的一刻，神舟十八号载人飞船在万众瞩目中顺利升空，成功与空间站对接。这一辉煌时刻不仅展现了我国航天科技的雄厚实力，更激发了经管学子的爱国热情。为了让学生直观感受这一国家盛事，江西软件职业技术大学经济管理学院迅速行动，组织学生线上观看神舟十八号升空直播，通过这一特殊方式，对学生进行深刻的爱国教育，推崇科技强国理念。</span></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">晚，学院师生齐聚线上直播间，共同见证神舟十八号载人飞船的壮丽升空。直播画面清晰流畅，从火箭点火升空到飞船与空间站对接的每一个细节都尽收眼底。学生们屏息凝神，全神贯注地观看着直播，不时发出阵阵惊叹声。</span></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240430/1714454398561095820.png" title="1714454398561095820.png" alt="微信截图_20240430131011.png" width="584" height="322" style="max-width: 100%; height: 322px; width: 584px;"/><img src="http://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240430/1714454379085036564.png" title="1714454379085036564.png" alt="微信截图_20240430131011.png" width="1" height="1" style="max-width: 100%; height: 1px; width: 1px;"/></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;">（经管学院学生党员、发展对象、积极分子点赞神舟十八号顺利飞天）</p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240430/1714454510754020081.png" title="1714454510754020081.png" width="590" height="348" style="max-width: 100%; height: 348px; width: 590px;"/></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240430/1714454510786037420.png" title="1714454510786037420.png" width="594" height="368" style="max-width: 100%; height: 368px; width: 594px;"/></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240430/1714454510840009139.png" title="1714454510840009139.png" width="596" height="353" style="max-width: 100%; height: 353px; width: 596px;"/></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240430/1714454510901040767.png" title="1714454510901040767.png" width="597" height="355" style="max-width: 100%; height: 355px; width: 597px;"/></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716291075547073196.png" title="1716291075547073196.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-21 192946.png" width="592" height="466" style="width: 592px; height: 466px;"/></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716291205644050226.png" title="1716291205644050226.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-21 193406.png" width="591" height="485" style="width: 591px; height: 485px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716291527261054808.png" style="width: 611px; height: 562px;" title="1716291527261054808.png" width="611" height="562"/></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716291598426016025.png" title="1716291598426016025.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-21 193926.png" width="619" height="573" style="width: 619px; height: 573px;"/></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716291633547047489.png" title="1716291633547047489.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-21 193045.png" width="635" height="556" style="width: 635px; height: 556px;"/></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240430/1714454652451002896.png" title="1714454652451002896.png" width="641" height="358" alt="微信截图_20240430131221.png" style="max-width: 100%; height: 358px; width: 641px;"/></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);">（经济管理学院学子点赞神州十八号顺利飞天）</span></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">经济管理学院党总支书记蔡平在讨论会上发表讲话，强调爱国教育的重要性和科技强国理念的深刻内涵。他指出，神舟十八号载人飞船的成功发射是我国航天事业发展的重要里程碑，也是国家综合实力和科技水平不断提升的生动体现。作为新时代的大学生，应该树立正确的世界观、人生观和价值观，积极投身到国家建设和发展中去，为实现中华民族伟大复兴的中国梦贡献青春力量。</span></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="http://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240430/1714454747714001905.png" title="1714454747714001905.png" alt="微信截图_20240430131235.png" width="630" height="370" style="max-width: 100%; height: 370px; width: 630px;"/></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;">(经济管理学院召开讨论会）</p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240430/1714454804343049372.png" title="1714454804343049372.png" alt="微信截图_20240430131252.png" width="643" height="378" style="max-width: 100%; height: 378px; width: 643px;"/></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;">图源：人民日报</p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">未来，经济管理学院将继续发挥自身优势，结合国家重大事件和时事热点，组织开展更多形式多样的爱国教育和科技创新活动，为培养更多具有爱国情怀和创新精神的人才贡献力量。</span></p><p style="color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">在这个充满挑战与机遇的时代，我们相信经济管理学院的学生们将不负时代重托，以更加饱满的热情和更加坚定的信念，投身到国家建设和发展中去，为实现中华民族的伟大复兴而努力奋斗。</span></p>